<C>__{woman}
<D>__{he died before he could complete his lifelong dream.}
<P>__{(beat)}
<D>__{i intend to finish it for him.}
<A>__{a voice interrupts them, calling from the estate...}
<C>__{older man}
<D>__{elektra!}
<C>__{elektra}
<D>__{excuse me.}
<A>__{she walks away, the wind pressing her dress against her delicate figure. she looks brave and vulnerable as she walks back toward her father's grand house.}
